lgp.core.environment

Interface ComponentLoader<TComponent>

  • Type Parameters:
    TComponent - The type of component that this loader is able to load.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Module
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConfigurationLoader, ConstantLoader<T>, DatasetLoader<TData>, OperationLoader<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CsvDatasetLoader, DefaultOperationLoader, DoubleConstantLoader, GenericConstantLoader, JsonConfigurationLoader, YamlConfigurationLoader

    public ComponentLoader<TComponent>
extends Module

    A interface Module that is able to load components.

    The implementer controls how a component the loader is responsible for is loaded and consumers should be indifferent to the implementation details.

    See Also:
    interface Module
